# Second Brain Overview

This vault separates evidence from knowledge. Original documents live in
`10-originals/` and are never modified. MarkItDown projections live in
`20-converted/` and are retrieval substrate, not truth. This folder,
`30-curated/`, holds the only notes that count as trusted knowledge —
reviewed by a human, linked back to their sources.

Agents retrieve through staged search (decisions first, raw conversions
last) and write their own observations to [[agent-memory]] under
`40-agent-memory/`, where they stay `unreviewed` until promoted.

Seeded by the installer as a working example of curated-note frontmatter —
edit or delete freely.
